posts.post_content:
Enhance your tea or coffee experience with these unique styled and good quality tea cups with your family or friends. Featuring an attractive and stylish design coffee mug from the Purezento Brand. These tea/coffee cups are best for serving coffee, Hot Chocolate, Green Tea, Black Tea, Green Tea, Masala Chai, Kawa and other hot beverages. These coffee mugs will be a wonderful addition to your home or office. These handcrafted crockery items are crafted by the best artisans in the pottery of India, keeping in mind to present you with the unique design for your kitchen and dining. Handle Design The Handle is designed in a way to give you a perfect grip while holding your beverage, so you can enjoy your drink with your partner. Tea/Coffee cup set is extremely durable and will last for a long time, even with regular use. Benefits of Ceramic Material Ceramic is generally considered among the healthiest materials used throughout the home, from cozy warm cups to tiled flooring
Hand-Painted Aesthetics and Easy to Hold: Our ceramic coffee mugs are elaborately designed of 
natural approach, exquisitely hand-painted with 4 kinds of diverse Japanese style patterns, which make these mugs unique and classic. There is ample space between the cup body and handle so you can hold it comfortably and evenly, and the big well-made handles won't get hot in the microwave,
Each cup brings you a tactile experience that delights the sense. It is functional without sacrificing artistry.
Handcrafted pottery cup with vintage speckles, fantastic pattern and shape with high quality.
It is safe for dishwasher, microwave, oven and freezer. Get this nice cup set as a thoughtful housewarming, holiday, birthday or anniversary gift for your families and friends.
✔️ Functional and Beautiful. Each Designer Mug holds 15 oz, Perfect for Coffee, Tea, Hot Chocolate, Cocoa or Soup. Great Gift for Holiday, Anniversary, Wedding, Mom & Dad, Couples, Friends & Lovers.
✔️ Durable Quality and Long-lasting Value. Perfect for Everyday Dining or Gourmet Events. Impress your Family & Friends with Stylish, Tasteful tableware designed for People who Enjoy Living Life Fully.
Easy To Clean and Non-Slip Bottom: The smooth glazed mug body prevents the coffee or tea stains remaining easily, rust-proof and scratch-resistant, which allows them to be simply wiped or handwashed. They are dishwasher, microwave, oven and freezer compatible. While the unglazed bottom is perfect to stop the cup slipping, safe to use
